 Adventures.png|Fan Rotom in [[Pokémon Adventures]]\nMow Rotom Adventures.png|Mow Rotom in [[Pokémon Adventures]]\n</gallery>\n\n===In the Pokémon Pocket Monsters manga===\n[[File:Rotom PMDP.png|thumb|210px|Rotom in [[Pokémon Pocket Monsters]]]]\nA Rotom appears in [[PMDP47]] in all of its forms.\n\n<gallery>\nHeat Rotom PMDP.png|Heat Rotom in [[Pokémon Pocket Monsters]]\nWash Rotom PMDP.png|Wash Rotom in [[Pokémon Pocket Monsters]]\nFrost Rotom PMDP.png|Frost Rotom in [[Pokémon Pocket Monsters]]\nFan Rotom PMDP.png|Fan Rotom in [[Pokémon Pocket Monsters]]\nMow Rotom PMDP.png|Mow Rotom in [[Pokémon Pocket Monsters]]\n</gallery>\n\n==In the TCG==\n{{main|Rotom (TCG)}}\n\n==Other appearances==\n===[[Super Smash Bros. Ultimate]]===\nRotom appears as a {{sbw|Spirits (characters)|Spirit}}.\n\n==Game data==\n===Pokédex entries===\n{{Dex/Header|type=Electric|type2=Ghost}}\n{{Dex/NA|gen=IV}}\n{{Dex/Gen/2|gen=IV|reg1=Sinnoh|num1=152|label1={{gameabbrev4|Pt}}:|reg2=Johto}}\n{{Dex/Entry2|v=Diamond|v2=Pearl|entry=Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.}}\n{{Dex/Entry1|v=Platinum|entry=Its electric-like body can enter some kinds of machines and take control in order to make mischief.}}\n{{Dex/Entry2|v=HeartGold|v2=SoulSilver|entry=Research continues on this Pokémon, which could be the power source of a unique motor.}}\n|}\n|}\n{{Dex/Gen/1|gen=V|reg1=Unova}}\n{{Dex/Entry2|v=Black|v2=White|t=FFF|entry=Its electric-like body can enter some kinds of machines and take control in order to make mischief.}}\n{{Dex/Entry2|v=Black 2|v2=White 2|t=FFF|entry=Its electric-like body can enter some kinds of machines and take control in order to make mischief.}}\n|}\n|}\n{{Dex/Gen/2|gen=VI|reg1=Kalos|num1=068|label1=Mountain|reg2=Hoenn}}\n{{Dex/Entry1|v=X|t=FFF|entry=Research continues on this Pokémon, which could be the power source of a unique motor.}}\n{{Dex/Entry1|v=Y|entry=Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electro